## Konteks
Plan: section 4.3 & 5 (V20). Entity `MailArchive` saat ini **schema mismatch berat** dengan legacy. Perlu rename @Column massal + ADD field legacy yang sebelumnya dibuang + DROP field tidak ada di legacy + tambah audit + FK + indexes.

> **WARNING:** rename @Column akan **memengaruhi semua JOOQ query** yang select kolomnya. Audit `repository/archive/jooq/` sebelum apply.

## Tabel target
- `mail_archive` (39,892 rows)

## Pre-flight check
```sql
SHOW CREATE TABLE mail_archive;  -- konfirmasi nama kolom legacy
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM mail_archive WHERE ma_mcat_id IS NOT NULL
  AND ma_mcat_id NOT IN (SELECT mcat_id FROM mail_category);
-- Expected: ~202
```

## SQL DDL — Flyway V20

File: `src/main/resources/db/migration/V20__mail_archive_align_legacy_columns.sql`

```sql
-- Step 1: audit column
ALTER TABLE mail_archive
  ADD COLUMN ma_updated_date DATETIME NULL AFTER ma_archive_date;

UPDATE mail_archive SET ma_updated_date = ma_archive_date
  WHERE ma_updated_date IS NULL;

-- Step 2: cleanup orphan ma_mcat_id
UPDATE mail_archive SET ma_mcat_id = NULL
  WHERE ma_mcat_id IS NOT NULL
    AND ma_mcat_id NOT IN (SELECT mcat_id FROM mail_category);

-- Step 3: FK
ALTER TABLE mail_archive
  ADD CONSTRAINT fk_archive_category
    FOREIGN KEY (ma_mcat_id) REFERENCES mail_category(mcat_id)
    ON DELETE SET NULL ON UPDATE CASCADE;

-- Step 4: indexes (gantinya partition)
CREATE INDEX idx_archive_ref_mail ON mail_archive(ma_ref_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_archive_status_date ON mail_archive(ma_status, ma_mail_date);
CREATE INDEX idx_archive_org ON mail_archive(ma_org_id);
```

## Entity diff — RENAME @Column massal
File: `entity/core/MailArchive.java`

| Java field | Sebelum `@Column(name=)` | Sesudah |
|---|---|---|
| `archiveDate` | `ma_date` | **`ma_mail_date`** |
| `mailId` | `ma_mail_id` | **`ma_ref_id`** |
| `category` | `ma_category` | **`ma_mcat_id`** |
| `createdDate` | `ma_created_date` | **`ma_archive_date`** |
| `createdByName` | `ma_created_by_name` | **`ma_archive_by_name`** |
| `officeCode` | `ma_office_code` | **`office_code`** (tanpa prefix!) |
| `location.rack` | `ma_rack` | **`ma_loc_rack`** |
| `location.shelf` | `ma_shelf` | **`ma_loc_tier`** |
| `location.box` | `ma_box` | **`ma_loc_box`** |
| `location.folderPosition` | `ma_folder_pos` | **DROP field** |
| `keywordFlag` | `ma_keyword_flag` | **`ma_keyword_index_flag`** |

### Field DIDROP dari entity
- `createdBy Integer` → andalkan `ma_archive_by_name`
- `attachmentQty` → query attachments table on-the-fly (atau view)
- `year` → derive `YEAR(ma_mail_date)` di service
- `publishedAt` → sama dengan `ma_archive_date`

### Field DITAMBAH ke entity (legacy yang sayang dibuang)
```java
@Column(name = "ma_mcat_type") private Integer mcatType;
@Column(name = "ma_mcat_code", length = 32) private String mcatCode;
@Column(name = "ma_org_code", length = 16) private String orgCode;
@Column(name = "ma_org_id") private Integer orgId;
@Column(name = "ma_ref_no", length = 45) private String refNo;
@Column(name = "ma_sent_to", length = 128) private String sentTo;
@Column(name = "ma_note", length = 512) private String note;
@Column(name = "ma_secret_type", length = 45) private String secretType;
@Column(name = "ma_keyword", columnDefinition = "TEXT") private String keyword;

// Embedded ArchiveLocation:
@Column(name = "ma_loc_building") private Integer building;
@Column(name = "ma_loc_floor") private Integer floor;
@Column(name = "ma_loc_room") private Integer room;
```

### Field BARU
```java
@UpdateTimestamp
@Column(name = "ma_updated_date") private LocalDateTime updatedDate;
```

### Embedded `ArchiveLocation` updates
- ADD: `building`, `floor`, `room` (Integer)
- RENAME: `shelf` → `tier` (`@Column(name="ma_loc_tier")`)
- DROP: `folderPosition`

## Files yang harus diaudit (HIGH RISK)
- `entity/core/MailArchive.java`
- `entity/core/embeddable/ArchiveLocation.java` (atau lokasi)
- **`repository/.../jooq/archive/*.java`** ← AUDIT SEMUA, semua referensi `MA_DATE`, `MA_MAIL_ID`, `MA_CATEGORY`, `MA_CREATED_DATE`, `MA_OFFICE_CODE`, `MA_RACK`, `MA_SHELF`, `MA_BOX`, `MA_FOLDER_POS`, `MA_KEYWORD_FLAG` perlu rename atau drop
- `repository/.../jpa/MailArchiveRepository.java`
- `service/.../MailArchive*Service`
- `dto/archive/*` — semua field yang di-expose harus disesuaikan
- `mapper/MailArchiveMapper` (MapStruct)
- Test fixture

## Langkah pengerjaan
1. Pre-flight: konfirmasi nama kolom legacy + orphan count.
2. Backup: `CREATE TABLE mail_archive_backup_20260504 AS SELECT * FROM mail_archive;`
3. Buat Flyway V20.
4. Refactor entity `MailArchive` (rename + add + drop) + `ArchiveLocation`.
5. **Refactor JOOQ queries** — fail-fast: regen JOOQ class dulu (`./gradlew jooqCodegen`), compile error akan menunjukkan lokasi yang harus diperbaiki.
6. Refactor MapStruct mapper.
7. Refactor DTO.
8. Update test fixture.
9. Run full test suite: `./gradlew test`.
10. Smoke test list/detail/create archive di staging.

## Rollback
```sql
ALTER TABLE mail_archive DROP FOREIGN KEY fk_archive_category;
DROP INDEX idx_archive_ref_mail ON mail_archive;
DROP INDEX idx_archive_status_date ON mail_archive;
DROP INDEX idx_archive_org ON mail_archive;
ALTER TABLE mail_archive DROP COLUMN ma_updated_date;
```

## Acceptance criteria
- [ ] Pre-flight match plan
- [ ] Backup ada
- [ ] V20 apply clean
- [ ] FK + 3 indexes ada
- [ ] Entity rename + add + drop selesai
- [ ] JOOQ query semua compile + pass test
- [ ] DTO + mapper updated
- [ ] Smoke test archive flow OK

## Blocked by
- bd #1 (preflight)
- bd #2 (OQ-2: ma_ref_id semantik) — opsional untuk decide FK ma_ref_id (tidak di-FK di V20)

## Konteks
Plan: section 4.4 & 5 (V21). `mail_archive_access.pos_id` di legacy adalah `varchar(20)`, di entity `Integer`. Perlu convert column type setelah verifikasi semua nilai numeric. Lalu drop field entity yang tidak ada di legacy + tambah field permission boolean.

## Tabel target
- `mail_archive_access` (119,619 rows)

## Pre-flight check (CRITICAL)
```sql
-- Wajib 0
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM mail_archive_access
  WHERE pos_id NOT REGEXP '^[0-9]+$' AND pos_id IS NOT NULL AND pos_id <> '';

-- Konfirmasi tidak ada orphan
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM mail_archive_access
  WHERE mail_archive_id NOT IN (SELECT ma_id FROM mail_archive);
-- Expected: 0
```

**Jika non-numeric > 0:** STOP — buka issue baru untuk handle nilai non-numeric (mungkin perlu di-NULL-kan atau tabel mapping).

## SQL DDL — Flyway V21

File: `src/main/resources/db/migration/V21__mail_archive_access_pos_id_int_and_fk.sql`

```sql
-- Backup
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS mail_archive_access_backup_20260504 AS
SELECT * FROM mail_archive_access;

-- Step 1: convert column type (asumsi pre-flight 0 non-numeric)
ALTER TABLE mail_archive_access
  MODIFY pos_id INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0;

-- Step 2: FK
ALTER TABLE mail_archive_access
  ADD CONSTRAINT fk_archive_access_archive
    FOREIGN KEY (mail_archive_id) REFERENCES mail_archive(ma_id)
    ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE;
```

## Entity diff
File: `entity/.../MailArchiveAccess.java`

### DROP
```diff
- private Integer accessLevel;
- private LocalDateTime grantedDate;
- private Integer grantedBy;
```

### ADD field permission (legacy: 1 char Y/N/' ')
```java
@Convert(converter = YesNoBooleanConverter.class)
@Column(name = "access", length = 1)
private Boolean canAccess;

@Convert(converter = YesNoBooleanConverter.class)
@Column(name = "download", length = 1)
private Boolean canDownload;

@Convert(converter = YesNoBooleanConverter.class)
@Column(name = "history", length = 1)
private Boolean canViewHistory;
```

### Converter baru: `util/YesNoBooleanConverter.java`
```java
@Converter
public class YesNoBooleanConverter implements AttributeConverter<Boolean, String> {
    @Override
    public String convertToDatabaseColumn(Boolean value) {
        return Boolean.TRUE.equals(value) ? "Y" : " ";
    }
    @Override
    public Boolean convertToEntityAttribute(String dbValue) {
        return "Y".equalsIgnoreCase(dbValue);
    }
}
```

## Files yang harus diaudit
- `entity/.../MailArchiveAccess.java`
- `util/YesNoBooleanConverter.java` (baru)
- `repository/.../jpa/MailArchiveAccessRepository.java`
- `repository/.../jooq/MailArchiveAccessQueryRepository.java` — kolom `POS_ID` tipe baru INT (regen JOOQ)
- `service/.../MailArchiveAccessService` — logic grant/revoke pakai boolean
- `dto/.../MailArchiveAccess*` — `canAccess`, `canDownload`, `canViewHistory` Boolean

## Langkah pengerjaan
1. Pre-flight CRITICAL: jika non-numeric > 0 STOP.
2. Backup table.
3. Buat Flyway V21.
4. Buat converter `YesNoBooleanConverter`.
5. Refactor entity (drop + add permission boolean).
6. Regen JOOQ.
7. Refactor service: grant ≈ set canAccess=true.
8. Refactor DTO.
9. Test: `./gradlew test --tests "*ArchiveAccess*"`.
10. Smoke test grant/revoke akses archive.

## Rollback
```sql
ALTER TABLE mail_archive_access DROP FOREIGN KEY fk_archive_access_archive;
ALTER TABLE mail_archive_access MODIFY pos_id VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0';
```

## Acceptance criteria
- [ ] Pre-flight: 0 non-numeric pos_id
- [ ] Backup ada
- [ ] V21 apply clean — pos_id INT
- [ ] FK ada
- [ ] Converter `YesNoBooleanConverter` ada + tested
- [ ] Entity field baru: canAccess/canDownload/canViewHistory
- [ ] Smoke test grant/revoke OK

## Blocked by
- bd #1 (preflight) — wajib non-numeric = 0
- bd #2 (OQ — investigate kalau pre-flight gagal)

